library HighRiskReferralEvents version '1.0.0'
using FHIR version '4.0.1'
include FHIRHelpers version '4.0.1' called FHIRHelpers include DataElements version '1.0.0' called DataElements include CDSConnectCommonsforFHIRv401 version '1.0.0' called C3F include BCSMCommonFunctions version '1.0.0' called BCSMCommon include CSMCommonFunctions version '1.0.0' called Common
codesystem "LOCAL": 'http://cancerscreeningcds.github.io/bcsm-cds/CodeSystem/screening-observation-code-system' codesystem "ActCode": 'http://cancerscreeningcds.github.io/bcsm-cds/CodeSystem/plan-definition-action-code-system'
code "High 5 year risk": 'high5yrisk' from "LOCAL" display 'High 5 year risk' code "5 year risk at least 1.67%": 'higherthanaverage5yrisk' from "LOCAL" display '5 year risk at least 1.67%'
context Patient
define "eve-ageAny": true
define "eve-ageAtLeast35": AgeInYears() >= 35
define "eve-geneticriskpop": DataElements."de-geneticrisk"
define "eve-chestxrtpop": DataElements."de-chestxrtage10to30"
define "eve-atypicalbxpop": DataElements."de-atypicalbx"
define "eve-LifeExp": DataElements."de-lifeexp"
define "eve-fiveyrriskpop": MostRecent5YrRiskAssessmentResultHigh is not null
define "eve-fiveyrrisklowpop": MostRecent5YrRiskAssessmentResultHigherThanAverage is not null
define "eve-fhxbrca": DataElements."de-fhxbreastcarisk" or DataElements."de-fhxrisk"
define "eve-personalriskfactors": if DataElements.MostRecentPersonalRiskFactorAssessment is not null then FHIRHelpers.ToBoolean(DataElements.MostRecentPersonalRiskFactorAssessment.value as boolean) else Count(DataElements."BiopsyDiagnosticReports") > 1 or DataElements."de-breastdensitycord"
define MostRecent5YrRiskAssessmentResultHigh: DataElements.MostRecent5YrRiskAssessment R where R.value as FHIR.Quantity is not null and C3F.QuantityValue(R).value >=3 or R.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept is not null and C3F.ConceptValue(R) ~ "High 5 year risk"
define MostRecent5YrRiskAssessmentResultHigherThanAverage: DataElements.MostRecent5YrRiskAssessment R where R.value as FHIR.Quantity is not null and C3F.QuantityValue(R).value >=1.67 and C3F.QuantityValue(R).value <3 or R.value as FHIR.CodeableConcept is not null and C3F.ConceptValue(R) ~ "5 year risk at least 1.67%"
// 5 year assessment is valid if done within past 5 years // and risk factor observation not changed from false to true after risk assessment define ValidMostRecent5YrRiskAssessment: DataElements."MostRecent5YrRiskAssessment" is not null and DataElements."MostRecent5YrRiskAssessmentDate" >= (Today() - 5 years) and RiskFactorModifiedAfterRiskAssessment is false
define RiskFactorModifiedAfterRiskAssessment: if "eve-fhxbrca" and LastFamilialRiskAssessmentObservationResult is false and Common.ObservationDate(DataElements.MostRecentFamilialRiskAssessmentObservation) is not null and Common.ObservationDate(DataElements.MostRecentFamilialRiskAssessmentObservation) > DataElements."MostRecent5YrRiskAssessmentDate" then true else if "eve-personalriskfactors" and LastPersonalRiskFactorObservationResult is false and Common.ObservationDate(DataElements.MostRecentPersonalRiskFactorAssessment) is not null and Common.ObservationDate(DataElements.MostRecentPersonalRiskFactorAssessment) > DataElements."MostRecent5YrRiskAssessmentDate" then true else false
define LastFamilialRiskAssessmentObservationResult: BCSMCommon.SortedObservations( DataElements.FamilialRiskAssessmentObservations )[1].value
define LastPersonalRiskFactorObservationResult: BCSMCommon.SortedObservations( DataElements.PersonalRiskFactorAssessments )[1].value
